case_circumstances:
This is a Dekalb County Police Department case, assisted by the NCMEC.  Tips/leads can be sent to NCMEC or the Dekalb PD at 770-724-7890.

On February 26, 1999, the skeletal remains of a young black male were discovered in a wooded area of a subdivision in Dekalb County, GA.
